<solution id="eip-id2538314">
<para id="eip-id2538316">
We are given that <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>m</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo><m:msub><m:mi>m</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">≡</m:mo><m:mi>m</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>. The given equations then become:</para>
<equation id="eip-id1899177"><m:math>

          <m:mrow>
